<!--
# Frozen Lake Run - Q-Table Inference

A greedy agent walks the 4x4 frozen-lake grid using the trained Q-table; run `frozen_lake_train.bsx` first to generate it.

    beet --main=examples/ml/frozen_lake_run.bsx
-->
